    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Epitobrilus interstitialis sp. n. Holotype male and paratype female. A:male head; B: vulva region; C: spicule and gubernaculum;D:supplement;E:female tail; F:male tail.Scalebars:B,E—90 µm; F—60 µm; A—40 µm; C—30 µm; D—15 µm." ;
