<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1064576>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Epitobrilus interstitialis sp. n. Holotype male, paratype male and female. A: male, entire body; B: female, entire body; C: male, anterior body end; D: vulva region; E, F: male head; G: female head; H: male, body at supplement region; I: male posterior body end; J: female tail.Scale bars:A, B—500 µm; C—200µm; D, H—100 µm; G, I, J—50 µm; E, F—20 µm." ;
